review:
Perfect treatment for dental queries
Surgery done to mark
Highly recommended
Clean clinic
Thanks Dr Sonali

Dr.Sonali has treated me for many of my dental issues, treatment is
excellent and very comfortable too.Both my children have got their treatment done successfully from Dr.Sonali, right diagnosis and best treatment plan for teeth alignment and wisdom tooth issues.

Dr sonali has treated me for teeth alignment and braces procedures. I was in severe need for treatment and Dr Sonali provided that service. I had a speedy treatment and great visible progress over a short period of time. I was anxious about braces and the myths of pain and discomfort but I saw that with the right doctor and help it was an easy procedure which helps greatly. Very impressed with results I've seen and thanks to Dr Sonali for providing excellent service.
Very experienced Dr SonaliPerfect extraction of teeth at reasonable costA root canal done in painless one sitting was doneNice clinicHighly recommended
Friendly and gentle dentist who took the time to explain everything. Painless cleaning and filling. Would recommend to anyone.
